<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677827>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Amathia acervata Lamouroux, 1824, holotype, Herbarium Sheet 86, MNHN, Paris. A. Entire type specimen. B. Original label in Lamouroux’s handwriting. C. Reconstituted fragment of holotype. D. Part of C, direct illumination. E, F. Part of C, in transmitted light, E showing distinct sinuosity of stolon within the autozooid cluster (same scale)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3677827/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

